** Ubuntu Notes **

Update

sudo apt update -y && sudo apt full-upgrade -y && sudo apt autoremove -y && sudo apt clean -y && sudo apt autoclean -y

Reboot

sudo shutdown -r +1

Change SSH Port

sudo nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config

Change Time Zone

timedatectl

sudo timedatectl set-timezone America/New_York

Save SSH History

history -w ~/history.txt

